com.interpss.simu.multicase.modify

Interface BaseValueChange

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ComplexValueChange, DoubleValueChange
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseValueChangeImpl, ComplexValueChangeImpl, DoubleValueChangeImpl

    public interface BaseValueChange
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Base Value Change'. Base class for defining value change

    The following features are supported:

    • Change Type
    • Percent
    • Unit
    See Also:
    MCaseModifyPackage.getBaseValueChange()
